text: Château de Dietrich, Reichshoffen The Château de Dietrich is a château in the commune of Reichshoffen, Bas-Rhin, Alsace, France. It was built in 1770 and was registered as a monument historique in 1940. ==References== Category:Châteaux in Bas-Rhin Category:Monuments historiques of Bas-Rhin
title: Château de Dietrich
